Titolo: Kero Blaster

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Kero Blaster (ケロブラスター) is a platform video game created by Daisuke "Pixel" Amaya. It was released in 2014 for PC and iOS and is the first major project of Pixel since Cave Story in 2004. The game places a heavy emphasis on shooting and received positive reviews on both platforms. A short, free demo titled Pink Hour was made available a month before the full game's release. A short free companion game and sequel to Pink Hour  titled Pink Heaven was released in November 2015, coinciding with the new Kero Blaster update.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 79
